                <h1>Protect Yourself: Identity Theft & Background Checks</h1>
                <p>Background check identity theft occurs when someone unlawfully uses another person's personal information, often leading to fraudulent activities. This can severely damage credit ratings and ruin lives. Preventative measures include monitoring credit reports, using identity theft protection services, and safeguarding personal information online.</p>
